    "updated_at": "2025-11-17T20:42:43Z",
    "body": "This issue appears to be a duplicate of #4024.\n\nI've updated PR #5071 which fixes this problem by ensuring both `display_dir` and `repo_root` are contracted with the home symbol before path comparison. This prevents the directory duplication you're seeing.\n\nThe PR has been rebased on the latest `master` and now includes a comprehensive test case for this scenario. Could you please test with the branch from PR #5071 and confirm it resolves your issue?",
    "author_association": "NONE",
